*steps to craete standalone app with gui and db:

1.create a Frontend
2.create a Backend
3.connect frontend with backend by attaching functions(backend) to the buttons(frontend)
4.install pyinstaller
	4.1 use link https://pypi.org/project/wheel/#files
	4.2 download and save file "wheel-0.34.2-py2.py3-none-any.whl"
	4.3 then #pip install wheel-0.34.2-py2.py3-none-any.whl
		or #pip install wheel
	4.4 #pip install pyinstaller
	4.4 #pyinstaller --onefile --windowed frontend.py
		#pyinstaller frontend.py
	4.5 check F:\Practice\app_library\dist\frontend.exe
	4.6 open exe or application file it will also create lite.db there.
	4.7 u can also copy ur db file in this dist folder for ur existing data in db.

